<CENTER><H2 ALIGN=CENTER>The First Epistle of Paul to the Thessalonians</H2>    
</CENTER><P><A HREF='index.htm'>Return to Index</A>.</P><CENTER><TABLE BORDER=0 
CELLPADDING=5 WIDTH=90%><TR><TD></TD><TD><CENTER><H1>Chapter 4</H1></CENTER>    
</TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V1><H4>1</H4></TD><TD><P>Furthermore then  
we beseech you, brethren, and exhort you by the ADONAY YAHSHUA, that as ye have 
received of us how ye ought to walk and to please ELOHIYM, so ye would abound   
more and more.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V2><H4>2</H4></TD><TD><P>
For ye know what commandments we gave you by the ADONAY YAHSHUA.</P></TD></TR>  
<TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V3><H4>3</H4></TD><TD><P>For this is the will of     
ELOHIYM, even your sanctification, that ye should abstain from fornication:</P> 
</TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V4><H4>4</H4></TD><TD><P>That every one of 
you should know how to possess his vessel in sanctification and honour;</P></TD>
</TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V5><H4>5</H4></TD><TD><P>Not in the lust of     
concupiscence, even as the Gentiles which know not ELOHIYM:</P></TD></TR><TR>   
<TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V6><H4>6</H4></TD><TD><P>That no man go beyond and       
defraud his brother in any matter: because that the ADONAY is the avenger of    
all such, as we also have forewarned you and testified.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD    
VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V7><H4>7</H4></TD><TD><P>For ELOHIYM hath not called us unto 
uncleanness, but unto holiness.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V8><H4> 
8</H4></TD><TD><P>He therefore that despiseth, despiseth not man, but ELOHIYM,  
who hath also given unto us his holy Spirit.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A 
NAME=V9><H4>9</H4></TD><TD><P>But as touching brotherly love ye need not that I 
write unto you: for ye yourselves are taught of ELOHIYM to love one another.</P>
</TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V10><H4>10</H4></TD><TD><P>And indeed ye   
do it toward all the brethren which are in all Macedonia: but we beseech you,   
brethren, that ye increase more and more;</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A    
NAME=V11><H4>11</H4></TD><TD><P>And that ye study to be quiet, and to do your   
own business, and to work with your own hands, as we commanded you;</P></TD>    
</TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V12><H4>12</H4></TD><TD><P>That ye may walk     
honestly toward them that are without, and that ye may have lack of nothing.</P>
</TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V13><H4>13</H4></TD><TD><P>But I would not 
have you to be ignorant, brethren, concerning them which are asleep, that ye    
sorrow not, even as others which have no hope.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP> 
<A NAME=V14><H4>14</H4></TD><TD><P>For if we believe that YAHSHUA died and rose 
again, even so them also which sleep in YAHSHUA will ELOHIYM bring with him.</P>
</TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V15><H4>15</H4></TD><TD><P>For this we say 
unto you by the word of the ADONAY, that we which are alive and remain unto the 
coming of the ADONAY shall not prevent them which are asleep.</P></TD></TR><TR> 
<TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V16><H4>16</H4></TD><TD><P>For the ADONAY himself shall  
descend from heaven with a shout, with the voice of the archangel, and with the 
trump of ELOHIYM: and the dead in MASHIYACH shall rise first:</P></TD></TR><TR> 
<TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V17><H4>17</H4></TD><TD><P>Then we which are alive and   
remain shall be caught up together with them in the clouds, to meet the ADONAY  
in the air: and so shall we ever be with the ADONAY.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD       
VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V18><H4>18</H4></TD><TD><P>Wherefore comfort one another     
with these words.</P></TD></TR></TABLE><!--This Software is copyright 2000 by   
